Package com.amazon.ata.debugging.subscribeandsave

Class App

java.lang.Object
com.amazon.ata.debugging.subscribeandsave.App
public class App
extends java.lang.Object
Provides inversion of control for the SNS MLP by instantiating all of the dependencies needed by the SubscriptionDebugUtil and its dependency classes.
